		<title>Bianchi: &#8216;Riforma reclutamento e contratto in tempi brevi&#8217;</title>
		<link>https://www.scuolainforma.it/2022/03/17/bianchi-riforma-reclutamento-e-contratto-in-tempi-brevi.html?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=bianchi-riforma-reclutamento-e-contratto-in-tempi-brevi</link>
		
